msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1944_10_courland/date"
msgid "8th October 1944 · South of Memel, Lithuania"
msgstr "8 de octubre de 1944 · Sur de Memel, Lituania"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1944_10_courland/doctrine_allround"
msgid "Doctrine: All-Round"
msgstr "Doctrina: completa"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1944_10_courland/doctrine_defensive"
msgid "Doctrine: Defensive"
msgstr "Doctrina: defensiva"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1944_10_courland/doctrine_irregular"
msgid "Doctrine: Irregular"
msgstr "Doctrina: irregular"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1944_10_courland/doctrine_offensive"
msgid "Doctrine: Offensive"
msgstr "Doctrina: ofensiva"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1944_10_courland/mission_option_select1"
msgid "Select your Doctrine for the mission:"
msgstr "Selecciona una doctrina para la misión:"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1944_10_courland/name"
msgid "Closing the Pocket"
msgstr "Tocando fondo"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1944_10_courland/name_big"
msgid "Closing the Pocket"
msgstr "Tocando fondo"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1944_10_courland/outro_completed"
msgid ""
"The glorious 43rd army completed the surrounding of Memel. During the "
"offensive, the German 3rd Panzer army HQ was overrun. Army group North had "
"been successfully trapped in North Courland."
msgstr "La encomiable 43.ª Armada terminó de rodear Memel. Durante la ofensiva, la sede del 3.er ejército Panzer fue invadida. El Grupo de Ejércitos Centro había quedado atrapado en North Courland."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1944_10_courland/outro_failed"
msgid ""
"This failure will prove very costly. The Germans now have the option to "
"either reinforce or evacuate their 3rd Panzer army! This means we will lose "
"countless more comrades than we already have. You will be in the front "
"echelon when we attack again!"
msgstr "Este fracaso nos va a salir caro. ¡Los alemanes ahora pueden o bien reforzarse o bien salvar a su 3.er ejército Panzer! Por lo tanto, vamos a perder muchos más camaradas de los que disponemos. ¡La próxima vez que ataquemos te tocará ir al frente!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1944_10_courland/narrator/officer/01"
msgid ""
"Comrades! Today is the day of reckoning for the Hitlerite hordes! Whilst our "
"glorious 5th guards tank army is breaching the Fascist defences around "
"Memel, we will secure this area and cut them off. "
msgstr "¡Camaradas! ¡Hoy será el fin del ejército hitleriano! Nuestra 5.ª Armada de Tanques de Guardia está hundiendo a las defensas fascistas que protegen Memel. Vamos a asegurar la zona y a repelerlos. "

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1944_10_courland/narrator/officer/02"
msgid ""
"The Germans attacked us last night, and today you are to counter-attack and "
"drive them out of this sector. "
msgstr "Anoche nos invadieron los alemanes. Hoy debes contratacar y expulsarlos del sector. "

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1944_10_courland/narrator/officer/03"
msgid "Expect high enemy presence, and they will be armed to the teeth!"
msgstr "¡Esperamos una gran presencia enemiga armada hasta los dientes!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1944_10_courland/narrator/officer/04"
msgid ""
"There are certain key locations in the area which High Command expects to be "
"captured. I will divert additional troops and resources to your command as "
"you progress with your mission. Good luck, comrades! Onward, to Victory!"
msgstr "Hay algunas ubicaciones importantes que el Alto Comando desea capturar. Conforme avances en la misión, iré asignándote tropas y recursos adicionales. ¡Buena suerte, camaradas! ¡Hacia la victoria, siempre!"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1944_10_courland/narrator/officer/05"
msgid ""
"The Luftwaffe may make an appearance. You must always advance with support "
"from  AA-guns. Our forward observers will inform when enemy ground-attack "
"aircraft are inbound."
msgstr "Puede que la Luftwaffe se presente, así que realiza maniobras de aproximación con el apoyo de cañones antiaéreos. Nuestros vigilantes nos informarán cada vez que los aviones enemigos planeen atacar."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1944_10_courland/narrator/officer/06"
msgid ""
"An enemy column is bound to arrive shortly, from the south! Get ready to "
"greet them!"
msgstr "¡En breves llegará una columna enemiga procedente del sur! ¡Prepárate para recibirla!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/01-rus/1944_10_courland/narrator/officer/task1_complete"
msgid "Good job. You now have access to supplies and logistical vehicles."
msgstr "Bien hecho. Ahora dispones de acceso a suministros y vehículos logísticos."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/01-rus/1944_10_courland/narrator/officer/task2_complete"
msgid "Excellent. AT-guns and other support weaponry are now at your disposal."
msgstr "Excelente. Los cañones antitanque y otro armamento de apoyo están a tu disposición."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/01-rus/1944_10_courland/narrator/officer/task3_complete"
msgid ""
"The Fascists have been driven out of the settlement once and for all! You "
"now have command of our medium tanks."
msgstr "¡Por fin hemos expulsado a los fascistas del asentamiento! Ahora estás al mando de nuestros tanques medianos."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/01-rus/1944_10_courland/narrator/officer/task4_complete"
msgid ""
"Nothing can stop our glorious Red Army. And now nothing will stop your heavy "
"tanks, Comrade. Use them wisely, we don't have many of them."
msgstr "Nada podrá detener al Ejército Rojo ni a tus tanques pesados, camarada. Úsalos con prudencia, no nos quedan muchos."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/01-rus/1944_10_courland/narrator/officer/task5_complete"
msgid ""
"Those miserable Hitlerite lowlives will no longer be able to bombard our "
"neighboring regiments. Comrade, I am giving you command of our long range "
"weaponry reserves."
msgstr "Se les acabó a las ratas de Hitler eso de bombardear nuestros regimientos vecinos. Camarada, dejo en tus manos las reservas de armamento de larga distancia."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/01-rus/1944_10_courland/narrator/officer/task6_complete"
msgid ""
"These Fascists have excellent radio equipment. We will use their equipment "
"to relay ground attack coordinates for our Sturmoviks."
msgstr "Los fascistas poseen una excelente comunicación por radio. La usaremos para transmitir a nuestros Sturmoviks coordenadas de ataques terrestres."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/01-rus/1944_10_courland/narrator/officer/task7_complete"
msgid ""
"The Enemy headquarters are ours. The end of the Fascist occupation is at "
"hand."
msgstr "La sede del enemigo ahora nos pertenece, se acerca el fin de la ocupación fascista."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1944_10_courland/place"
msgid "43rd Army"
msgstr "43.ª Armada"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1944_10_courland/task1"
msgid "Recapture the depot for acquiring supplies"
msgstr "Vuelve a capturar el depósito para adquirir suministros"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1944_10_courland/task2"
msgid ""
"Capture the first line of defence to get access to AT equipment and support "
"weaponry"
msgstr "Captura la primera línea defensiva para conseguir equipamiento AT y armamento de apoyo"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1944_10_courland/task3"
msgid "Recapture the village of Daukšaičiai to gain access to medium armour."
msgstr "Vuelve a capturar la aldea de Dauksaiciai para obtener acceso a blindaje mediano."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1944_10_courland/task4"
msgid "Secure the road checkpoint to pave way for our heavy tanks."
msgstr "Asegura el punto de control de la carretera para marcar el camino de nuestros tanques pesados."

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1944_10_courland/task5"
msgid ""
"Take out the German Heavy Artillery position and gain access to heavy "
"howitzers"
msgstr "Controla la posición de la artillería alemana pesada para obtener acceso a obuses pesados"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1944_10_courland/task6"
msgid ""
"Seize the enemy communications outpost to establish communications with our "
"air force"
msgstr "Hazte con el control del puesto de comunicación enemigo para comunicarte con nuestras tropas aéreas"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1944_10_courland/task7"
msgid "Assault the German headquarters and surrounding defences"
msgstr "Asalta la sede alemana y sus defensas colindantes"

msgctxt "mission/single/01-rus/1944_10_courland/story"
msgid "Army Group North suffers the unstoppable tide of the Red Army. Stavka proceeds to encircle the city of Memel. In the south, the 43rd Army dashes towards the coast to cut the Germans off from the south. A brutal engagement is about to unfold..."
msgstr "El Grupo de Ejércitos Norte es claramente superado por el Ejército Rojo. Stavka se dispone a rodear la ciudad de Memel. Mientras, al sur, la 43.ª Armada se dirige a la costa con la intención de echar a los alemanes. He aquí el comienzo de una batalla histórica..."
